    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "$46,900 - Exceptionally clean older vehicle in mint condition and about as nice as you\u2019ll find for its age. It shows extremely little wear inside and out, presents beautifully, and has clearly been very well cared for. The paint, interior, and overall appearance are outstanding, and it should appeal to a buyer looking for a top-tier example rather than just a basic driver. If you want an older vehicle that stands out for its condition and has been preserved unusually well, this is the kind of car to come see.",
