    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Clean, straightforward, and affordably priced, this vehicle is a practical choice for anyone seeking simple transportation without a major investment. It shows its age in places, but it remains a solid value with plenty of useful life for the right buyer. An excellent opportunity for a commuter, first-time buyer, or anyone needing a dependable extra vehicle at a budget-friendly price.",
