      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little runabout that\u2019s far from perfect, but it still starts up, gets you from A to B, and offers a lot of value for someone who needs affordable wheels. It shows its age and would suit a handy owner, a first-time buyer on a budget, or anyone after a cheap daily, backup car, or project. If you\u2019re looking for something low-cost with useful life left in it, this is well worth a look.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver with honest character and plenty of potential. Engine fires up, pulls through the rev range, and the drivetrain feels serviceable, making this a great candidate for someone wanting an affordable commuter, weekend project, or tuner platform. Shows cosmetic wear consistent with age, but the core package is there: straightforward mechanical layout, good parts availability, and room to improve while driving and enjoying it. If you want an inexpensive entry point into ownership with real upside, this one makes sense.",
      "price": 5895.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Honest poor-condition car priced to move. Strong value for a budget buyer, work truck, or project. First serious buyer gets it.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of honest, road-worn character you notice right away\u2014the sort of machine that feels like it still has stories left to tell. It\u2019s an ideal fit for someone who appreciates a hands-on project, needs an affordable set of wheels, or wants a platform with personality and possibility. There\u2019s a rugged charm here that makes it easy to imagine bringing it back into the spotlight, and at this price, it\u2019s a chance to own something with real presence without stretching the budget.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
